If you're looking for a quick escape near Shimla, **Kufri, Mashobra, and Chail** are perfect weekend destinations.

- **Kufri:** Start your day with a horse ride to **Mahasu Peak**, enjoy adventure activities at **Kufri Fun World**, and explore the **Himalayan Nature Park**.
- **Mashobra:** Hike through **lush cedar forests**, enjoy a peaceful retreat at **Craignano Nature Park**, and end your day with sunset views at **Reserve Forest Sanctuary**.
- **Chail:** Visit the **Chail Palace**, walk through the **world’s highest cricket ground**, and take in stunning valley views from **Kali Ka Tibba**.

Whether you seek adventure or relaxation, these spots offer the perfect weekend hustle. Plan your getaway with **Pahari Yatri** for a seamless experience!
